         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(lines 1-2) (They have decreed that) those posts and honorable offices and secretaryships of which they have paid the prices shall be secured to their owners. (lines 15-17) And they have decreed that no one shall be removed or forcibly ejected at those temples where rights of asylum subsisted.</ab>
